cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper focuses on improving the efficiency of deep neural networks for image classification tasks, specifically on the CIFAR10 dataset. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed method involves training decision gates to dynamically determine the depth of embeddings, which is a machine learning technique. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - Deep neural networks are a popular technique in AI, and the paper proposes a method to make them more efficient. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper deals with deep neural networks and their optimization, which falls under the scope of this sub-category. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a method to reduce the computational cost of deep neural networks, which involves optimizing the algorithms used for inference.
